{"lastModified":1770146911473,"uri":"c::19844607888::vessel::e93906b0-a903-11f0-84ea-7545bd984bb1","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Newport Beach Bay\n\nThis luxury mega yacht Lazzara 84 comes with a captain, deckhand and a host for $1000 per hour an preferred minimum booking of 4 hours in Newport Beach.\n\nSuper fun top of the line sound system lighting system and was fully redone 2021\n\nWe are proud to offer this fine yacht that has been kept in exceptional condition and well-maintained her entire life. A state-of-the-art design, the Lazzara 80 Motor Yacht is a sleek Euro-style luxury yacht that incorporates a host of innovative features.\n\nShe accommodates up to 12 guests in (6) luxurious staterooms, (1) king master suite, and (2) spacious queen VIP cabins on the lower level,(2) additional staterooms forward are perfect for additional guests or crew; Captain’s quarters are separate. All staterooms offer private heads as well as a day head that is just off the dining room. The formal dining area is lovely and the galley can be isolated from the salon by closing off the breakfast bar. A spiral staircase in the salon leads up to the bridge with its stylish hardtop.\n\nShe is equipped with a day head and the deck configuration has. Additional features include a den/office forward, a transom garage, a foredeck sun lounge, and walkaround side decks. Varied areas of entertaining promise a relaxing and most enjoyable voyage on this lovely Lazzara!\n\nhttps://www.facebook.com/reel/1636315333727305","blueprint":{"name":"LA VIE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::e93906b0-a903-11f0-84ea-7545bd984bb1::assets::ecb765c0-a908-11f0-937d-6779b8f1d749/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e93906b0-a903-11f0-84ea-7545bd984bb1::assets::58f57840-a908-11f0-bc6a-215e779a7322/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::e93906b0-a903-11f0-84ea-7545bd984bb1::assets::58f52a20-a908-11f0-8500-b1dffff2c053/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::